"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-nas-calls-for-logo-for-8th-national-astronomy-olympiad\", \"text\": \"Subscribe Now  KATHMANDU, Jan 25: Nepal Astronomical Society (NAS) has hosted a logo competition as part of its preparation for the Olympiad. The NAS has solicited calls for logo from January 24 to February 1, NAS Chairperson Suresh Bhattarai told RSS.  The best logo would be awarded a cash prize of Rs 5,000 along with a certificate. Also, the best logo would be the official logo of the '8th National Astronomy Olympiad, 2021'.  According to the NAS, it has been annually organizing logo competitions since 2013 as part of a public awareness campaign on the Olympiad. The NAS has opened the participation of logo designers in the competition being not limited to school-level participants.  Chairperson Bhattarai further informed that the competitors can submit their creations through the website www.nepalastronomicalsociety.org/olympiad.    Ballot Box Revolt: What RSP's breakthrough victory...  Warning, Threat or Opportunity? Nepal's major part...  Granary in crisis: Water politics leave Madhesh pa...  \\\"China stands ready to work with Nepal to carry forward the traditional friendship, deepen practical cooperation and advance bilateral relations\\\", read the statement.  Building Nepal's Digital Future  Fuel shortages in Nepal: A hidden threat to health a...  Second Innings of Balen and Gagan  Who will become Balen's climate pilot?  Three \\\"S\\\" factors-sulabhata (availability), sangat (peer influence), and siko (imitation)-are driving Madhesh's youth toward drug addiction.<...  Three \\\"S\\\" factors-sulabhata (availability), sangat (peer influence), and siko (imitation)-are driving Madhesh's youth toward drug addiction.<...  ANFA CEO Indraman Tuladhar said the ANFA submitted all necessary documents regarding foreign players' visas to the Ministry of Youth and Sports and the National Sports Council one and a half mon...  Nepal Republic Media Limite